    "metaDescription": "Explore how space, nature, and human life exist in harmony through Vastu Shastra. Discover conscious design and Vedic architecture principles.",
    "excerpt": "For thousands of years, Indian sages explored how space, nature, and human life exist in harmony. Discover how conscious design shapes our consciousness.",
