    "metaDescription": "At 7:00 a.m. in London, the CEO of a global technology company opened a resignation letter from one of the organisation's most respected leaders. It was the fif...",
    "excerpt": "At 7:00 a.m. in London, the CEO of a global technology company opened a resignation letter from one of the organisation's most respected leaders. It was the fif...",
    "category": "Spiritual Mentorship",
